            <p><font color = "#ff0000">Regardless, the use of AstroRad vests developed by NASA and a solar storm shelter developed by Elon Musk are realistic short-term solutions.</font></p>

            <p><font color = "#ff0000">Lead – thick and heavy – between a human being at the atmosphere on Mars have been shown to provide significant shielding from most radiation coming from space.</font></p>

